description: The story of Jody (Tyrese Gibson), a misguided, 20-year-old African-American who is really just a baby boy finally forced-kicking and screaming to face the commitments of real life. Streetwise and jobless, he has not only fathered two children by two different women-Yvette (Taraji P. Henson) and Peanut (Tamara LaSeon Bass) but still lives with his own mother. He can't seem to strike a balance or find direction in his chaotic life.

name: All Eyez on Me
title: 2017 ‧ Drama/Music ‧ 2h 19m
description: Tupac Shakur, a renowned American rapper, singer and actor, faces imprisonment, financial problems and fights with gang members and police while pursuing his career goals.

name: Do the Right Thing
title: 1989 ‧ Comedy/Drama ‧ 2 hours
description: In a Brooklyn neighbourhood, the long-simmering racial tensions between diverse communities erupt into brutal violence over the course of a single summer day.

name: King of New York
title: 1990 ‧ Crime/Thriller ‧ 1h 49m
description: Frank White, a former drug lord, returns to New York to destroy his competitors and steal from them. The money he acquires, he intends to distribute among the poor of the city.

name: Gridlock'd
title: 1997 ‧ Comedy/Crime ‧ 1h 31m
description: After a close friend dies from an overdose, two friends realise the importance of life. However, things take a turn as they attempt to curb their addiction.

name: Madea's Family Reunion
title: 2006 ‧ Comedy/Romance ‧ 2h 20m
description: Madea is a busy grandma with many responsibilities; firstly, she has to take care of the rebellious Nikki and also hold a family reunion. Will she be able to handle the reunion?

name: Madea's Big Happy Family
title: 2011 ‧ Comedy/Drama ‧ 1h 46m
description: Shirley learns that she is suffering from cancer and wishes to inform her children. But the relentless quarrelling among the siblings keeps getting in the way.

name: Diary of a Mad Black Woman
title: 2005 ‧ Comedy/Romance ‧ 1h 56m
description: After being married for 18 years, Helen's husband divorces her for another woman. Heartbroken, she moves in with her sassy grandmother who helps her overcome the trauma.

name: Scary Movie
title: 2000 ‧ Horror/Comedy ‧ 1h 28m
description: Cindy Campbell and her friends mistakenly end up killing a man. A year after the unfortunate incident, someone stalks them, leaves threatening messages and tries to murder them one by one.

name: Scary Movie 3
title: 2003 ‧ Comedy/Horror ‧ 1h 24m
description: Cindy Campbell comes across a cursed videotape that causes its viewer's death. She has strong suspicions that the tape is linked with the mysterious crop circles appearing on Tom Logan's farms.

name: Scary Movie 4
title: 2006 ‧ Comedy/Comedy horror ‧ 1h 31m
description: While working as a caretaker for an old woman, Cindy meets the ghost of a boy. She also falls in love with Tom, a neighbour. When giant tripods invade the Earth, Cindy decides to find some answers.

name: Halloween II
title: 1981 ‧ Horror/Crime ‧ 1h 32m
description: Myers, a horrific murderer, spends 15 years in an insane asylum after terrorising the people in his small hometown on the eve of a halloween. As soon as he gets out, he hunts down his sister.

name: Hotel Transylvania 2
title: 2015 ‧ Family/Comedy ‧ 1h 29m
description: Dracula becomes anxious for his beloved half-human, half-vampire grandson, Dennis, when he notices that he is not showing any signs of being a vampire.

name: Halloween: The Curse of Michael Myers
title: 1995 ‧ Horror/Crime ‧ 1h 36m
description: Michael Myers, the notorious masked murderer, returns to haunt Tommy Doyle, a young man who has a history with the killer and the Strode family.

name: RoboCop
title: 1987 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 42m
description: In a dystopian city infested with crime, terminally wounded police officer Alex Murphy returns from the brink of death as a cyborg law enforcer named RoboCop.

name: Predator 2
title: 1990 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 48m
description: Lieutenant Mike Harrigan and his police force try to hunt down a vicious alien hunter killing drug gangs in Los Angeles despite the warnings of a mysterious government agent.

name: RoboCop 2
title: 1990 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 2 hours
description: After a new drug surfaces and results in an outrageous increase in the crime rate, a new version of Robocop is created to bring the situation under control. But the faulty design makes him go rogue.

name: The Terminator
title: 1984 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 47m
description: The Terminator, a cyborg assassin from the future, attempts to find and kill Sarah Connor, a waitress who is destined to give birth to a man who will save humankind from extinction.

name: Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines
title: 2003 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 49m
description: A cybernetic soldier travels back in time in order to take John Connor, a drifter, to safety. Meanwhile, the soldier also has to save Connor's future wife as she is a key to humanity's salvation.

name: Terminator Salvation
title: 2009 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 55m
description: John Connor finds out about Skynet's new project, a powerful new model, T-800, that can wipe out the human race. Subsequently, he decides to lead an army against these destructive machines.

name: Judge Dredd
title: 1995 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 36m
description: In the year 2139, a judge is wrongly framed for a murder and sentenced to life imprisonment. His mentor informs him that he needs to stop a former judge from creating chaos in the society.

name: Terminator 2: Judgment Day
title: 1991 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 17m
description: When John, Sarah's 10-year-old son is attacked by T-1000, a new robot created by Skynet to destroy humanity, Terminator takes it upon himself to fight T-1000 to save John and the human race.

name: Zack Snyder's Justice League
title: 2021 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 4h 2m
description: Bruce Wayne and Diana Prince try to bring the metahumans of Earth together after the death of Clark Kent. Meanwhile, Darkseid sends Steppenwolf to Earth with a vast army to subjugate humans.

name: Alita: Battle Angel
title: 2019 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 2m
description: Alita, a battle cyborg, is revived by Ido, a doctor, who realises that she actually has the soul of a teenager. Alita then sets out to learn about her past and find her true identity.

name: Transporter 3
title: 2008 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 44m
description: Frank is forced to replace his friend after he dies while delivering a package. He must remain close to the car or it will explode, and make the delivery without getting killed in the bargain.

name: District 9
title: 2009 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 1h 52m
description: Wikus Van De Merwe, a government agent responsible for relocating the alien species living in the slums of Johannesburg, ends up becoming the target of a nationwide manhunt after a small mishap.

name: Dredd
title: 2012 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 35m
description: In a dystopic future, coldblooded policeman Dredd and psychic rookie Cassandra investigate three brutal murders in a tower block where they stumble upon a drug den run by the vicious drug lord Ma-Ma.

name: Predators
title: 2010 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 47m
description: A mixed bag of mercenaries and militia people find themselves on an alien planet that acts as a game preserve where they are being hunted. They must join forces to combat a merciless race of aliens.

name: Prey
title: 2022 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 39m
description: A skilled Comanche warrior protects her tribe from a highly evolved alien predator that hunts humans for sport, fighting against wilderness, dangerous colonisers and this mysterious creature to keep her people safe.

name: Rambo: Last Blood
title: 2019 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 40m
description: John Rambo's peaceful life is interrupted when Gabriela, his friend's granddaughter, disappears in Mexico. He decides to free her from the clutches of local cartels, starting a cycle of revenge.

name: Fast & Furious 6
title: 2013 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 10m
description: Hobbs is tasked with catching a team of mercenary drivers who manage to evade him every time. However, he enlists the help of Dominic and his team in exchange for full pardons for their past crimes.

name: Taxi
title: 1998 ‧ Comedy/Action ‧ 1h 30m
description: To work off his blemished driving record, a fashionable taxi driver, Daniel, must chauffeur an inept police inspector, Emilien, who is on the trail of German bank robbers.

name: Taxi 3
title: 2003 ‧ Comedy/Action ‧ 1h 30m
description: A police inspector and a detective enlist the help of a taxi driver to help them nab a gang of thieves wreaking havoc in the city. However, the team has to sort out their personal troubles first.

name: Taxi 4
title: 2007 ‧ Comedy/Action ‧ 1h 31m
description: A police officer who is tricked into letting a criminal go free loses his job but luckily his taxi-driver friend knows where the criminal is hiding out.The duo set out on a comic quest to capture him.

name: The Fate of the Furious
title: 2017 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 2h 16m
description: Dominic's idyllic life with Letty is interrupted when he is coerced by Cipher, a mysterious cyberterrorist, into betraying his team. The crew must now find Dom and Cipher before she unleashes chaos.

name: The Fast and the Furious
title: 2001 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 46m
description: A spate of high-speed robberies in LA brings street racer Dominic Toretto and his crew under the LAPD scanner. FBI agent Brian goes undercover and befriends Toretto in a bid to investigate the matter.

name: Fast & Furious
title: 2009 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 47m
description: Dominic, an ex-convict fugitive, comes across agent Brian when a crime case brings them back to LA. However, they must set aside their differences and confront their common enemy, a heroin smuggler.

name: The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift
title: 2006 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 44m
description: In order to avoid jail time, an errant car racer is sent to live with his father in Tokyo. However, he finds himself in trouble once again when he becomes a major competitor in drifting.

name: Phone Booth
title: 2002 ‧ Thriller/Action ‧ 1h 21m
description: Stu Shepard, a publicist, finds himself in a nightmarish situation when he answers a ringing phone at a phone booth. The mysterious caller threatens to shoot him if he cuts the call.

name: The Farewell
title: 2019 ‧ Comedy/Drama ‧ 1h 40m
description: A Chinese family learns that their grandmother has less time to live so they organise a wedding before her death. However, Billi is unhappy with the family's decision.

name: Past Lives
title: 2023 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 46m
description: Nora and Hae Sung, two deeply connected childhood friends, are wrest apart after Nora's family emigrates from South Korea. Decades later, they are reunited for one fateful week as they confront destiny, love and the choices that make a life.

name: Spotlight
title: 2015 ‧ Thriller/Crime ‧ 2h 8m
description: Martin Baron joins the Boston Globe as an editor and pushes four journalists named Michael, Walter, Sacha and Matt to pursue a story about the child molestation charges against the local church.

name: In Bruges
title: 2008 ‧ Comedy/Crime ‧ 1h 47m
description: Ray and Ken, two hitmen, get stuck in Bruges, Belgium, after an unsuccessful mission. The situation becomes even more complicated when their boss asks Ken to kill Ray.

name: Pan's Labyrinth
title: 2006 ‧ Fantasy/War ‧ 1h 59m
description: Ofelia moves with her mother to her stepfather's house. At night, a fairy leads her to a faun who informs her that she is a princess and she needs to participate in three tasks to prove her royalty.

name: Jackie Brown
title: 1997 ‧ Crime/Thriller ‧ 2h 34m
description: A flight attendant caught smuggling gun money has to choose between teaming up with the cops to bust her arms dealer boss or concealing the information and going to jail.

name: Pulp Fiction
title: 1994 ‧ Crime/Thriller ‧ 2h 34m
description: In the realm of underworld, a series of incidents intertwines the lives of two Los Angeles mobsters, a gangster's wife, a boxer and two small-time criminals.

name: They Cloned Tyrone
title: 2023 ‧ Mystery/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 2m
description: A series of eerie events thrusts an unlikely trio onto the trail of a nefarious government conspiracy.

name: Being John Malkovich
title: 1999 ‧ Comedy/Fantasy ‧ 1h 52m
description: A puppeteer takes up a job to support his family. While working late one night, he finds a portal that leads directly to the head of the Hollywood actor John Malkovich.

name: The Rookie
title: 2018 ‧ Drama ‧ 6 seasons
description: Forty-year-old John Nolan moves to Los Angeles in the hope of becoming a police officer. However, he is met with scepticism from all corners and must battle many challenges along the way.

name: Law & Order: Organized Crime
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 4 seasons
description: After suffering a grave personal loss detective Elliot Stabler returns to the NYPD determined to take down an organised crime ring.

name: Catching Killers
title: 2020 ‧ Documentary ‧ 1 season
description: Uncovering every clue and chasing every lead to solve cases and take down the most deadly criminals.

name: Catch Me a Killer
title: 2024 ‧ Crime ‧ 1 season
description: Micki returns to Cape Town to work on a new case; a serial killer targets prostitutes; a potential suspect emerges, but extracting a confession becomes a race against time.

name: Donkerbos
title: 2022 ‧ Thriller
description: When the bodies of six children are found in the backwater forests of Donkerbos, Limpopo, an ostracised detective must wrestle with her dark past, her family and a distrustful community to catch the killer before another child is taken.

name: Devilsdorp
title: 2021 ‧ Documentary ‧ 1 season
description: In 2016, a series of mysterious, brutal killings grips the town of Krugersdorp, South Africa. Known as the "Appointment Murders", the investigation leads detectives to a series of cold cases connected to a Satanic cult.

name: Blood & Water
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 4 seasons
description: After crossing paths at a party, a Cape Town teen sets out to prove whether a private-school swimming star is her sister who was abducted at birth.

name: The Chelsea Detective
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: London's Chelsea neighborhood is a beautiful borough for beautiful people, but it has a dark underside of deception, violence, greed and murder. Bodies have a way of showing up, and things are rarely what they seem.

name: No Offence
title: 2015 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: A group of police officers try their best to keep the streets of Manchester free of crime. When all else fails, they decide to use unconventional methods to teach the perpetrators a lesson.

name: High Country
title: 2024 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Detective Andie Whitford gets transferred to the High Country, where she is tasked with investigating the mysterious disappearances of five locals lost in the Victorian wilderness.

name: Whitstable Pearl
title: 2021 ‧ Mystery ‧ 2 seasons
description: Pearl Nolan, a single mother and restaurant owner, begins a private detective agency. Soon, she finds herself embroiled in a case after a close friend dies under mysterious circumstances.

name: ZeroZeroZero
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: The 'Ndrangheta, a Mafia organisation, faces disorder when the boss's position is challenged by his grandson. As a result of the discord, an important shipment of drugs is rerouted to Africa.

name: Gomorrah
title: 2014 ‧ Drama ‧ 5 seasons
description: Ciro di Marzio, the right-hand man of gangster Don Pietro, wishes to rise to power and gain control of the Savastano clan. He soon seizes his opportunity after Don Pietro's arrest.

name: Happy Valley
title: 2014 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: Catherine Cawood, a no-nonsense police sergeant in a rural Yorkshire valley, inadvertently finds herself involved in something significantly different than her job.

name: Grantchester
title: 2014 ‧ Drama ‧ 9 seasons
description: Sidney Chambers, a clergyman, decides to become an investigator when a parishioner is found murdered under mysterious circumstances. He teams up with Inspector Geordie to solve various criminal cases.

name: Drugs, Inc.
title: 2010 ‧ Documentary ‧ 7 seasons
description: How does the drug trade work? Can it be stopped or should it be regulated? And what are the personal costs? Those are just some of the questions asked in this series, a comprehensive look at society's most abused drugs: cocaine, methamphetamine, heroin and marijuana. First-person perspectives from traffickers, dealers, users, law enforcement and medical professionals detail how the drugs are processed and moved onto the streets, and the effects they have on the human body. It's a raw, eye-opening documentary about a billion-dollar industry.

name: Luna Park
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: In 1960s Rome, a free-spirited young woman who's grown up at her family's circus unexpectedly discovers she belongs to two very different worlds.

name: The Bad Guy
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Nino Scotellaro, a Sicilian prosecutor, dedicates his entire life to fighting the Mafia but is suddenly accused of being part of it; after being convicted, Nino decides to set up a Machiavellian revenge plan.

name: House
title: 1985 ‧ Horror/Comedy ‧ 1h 33m
description: After his aunt's funeral, Roger, a writer, decides to spend time in her house and complete his novel about the Vietnam War. But soon, he begins to experience strange paranormal activities.

name: Ghostbusters
title: 1984 ‧ Comedy/Horror ‧ 1h 45m
description: When Peter Venkman, Raymond Stantz and Egon Spengler lose their jobs as scientists, they start an establishment called Ghostbusters to fight the evil ghosts lurking in New York City.

name: Scream Queens
title: 2015 ‧ Horror ‧ 2 seasons
description: Kappa House at Wallace University is a sorority that prefers to enrol only the most elite. However, when the dean issues orders that the house should be open to all, a bloody mayhem ensues.

name: Are You Afraid of the Dark?
title: 1990 ‧ Horror ‧ 7 seasons
description: Young members of the Midnight Society meet weekly and narrate horror tales. However, their world turns upside down when some of the ghostly stories start occurring in real life.

name: American Horror Story
title: 2011 ‧ Horror ‧ 12 seasons
description: Sister Jude, a nightclub-singer-turned-nun, works at the Briarcliff Mental Institution in Massachusetts. She believes that God has chosen her to destroy evil by killing the inmates of the asylum.

name: Archive 81
title: 2022 ‧ Horror ‧ 1 season
description: An archivist takes a job restoring damaged videotapes, but finds themselves getting pulled into a mystery involving the missing director and a mysterious cult that they were documenting.

name: Guillermo del Toro's Cabinet of Curiosities
title: 2022 ‧ Horror ‧ 1 season
description: An anthology of sinister stories told by revered horror creators.

name: Gothika
title: 2003 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 38m
description: A psychiatrist awakens as a patient in a mental institution, with no memory of the murder she's accused of committing. As she tries to regain her memory, a vengeful spirit manipulates her.

name: The Sixth Sense
title: 1999 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 47m
description: Cole Sear, a troubled child, is gifted with a unique power to communicate with the dead. He consults an equally disturbed psychologist, Dr. Malcolm Crowe, to help him out of this strange problem.

name: The Orphanage
title: 2007 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 45m
description: Laura and her family move into what used to be her former orphanage. Soon, her adopted son, Simon, tells her that he has five invisible friends. But, his seemingly innocent games take a nasty turn.

name: The Amityville Horror
title: 2005 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 30m
description: George and Kathy move into a new home along with their kids. They're happy they've got a large and beautiful house at a bargain price. This is until bizarre and unexplainable events begin to occur.

name: The Omen
title: 1976 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 51m
description: Robert, a married man, agrees to switch his wife's stillborn baby with an orphaned infant. But as the child grows, a sinister series of events start taking place.

name: Omen III: The Final Conflict
title: 1981 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 48m
description: Antichrist Damien Thorn becomes US Ambassador to Britain, and is bent on total world domination.

name: The Terminal List
title: 2022 ‧ Thriller ‧ 1 season
description: James Reece returns home after his entire platoon of Navy SEALs is ambushed, only to discover new dark forces working against him and endangering the ones he loves.

name: FUBAR
title: 2023 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: A CIA operative on the verge of retirement discovers a family secret and is forced to go back into the field for one last job.

name: Hacks
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: A strange mentorship develops when a legendary comedian struggling to hold on to her dwindling empire hires a young unemployed writer to liven up her material.

name: Mad Max: Fury Road
title: 2015 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2 hours
description: In an apocalyptic world, a tyrant rules over a stark desert, controlling every drop of water. Two rebels, one escaping grief and the other reaching out to her childhood, are the last hope for a few.

name: Mad Max
title: 1979 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 33m
description: Max Rockatansky, a member of a police unit, confronts a gangster that results in the gangster being killed. The gang leader decides to avenge his mate's death.

name: The Wolverine
title: 2013 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 6m
description: Logan travels to Tokyo to meet Yashida, an old acquaintance who is dying. The situation regresses when Yashida offers to take away his healing abilities, but Logan refuses.

name: X-Men: Days of Future Past
title: 2014 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 31m
description: Wolverine time-travels to 1973 to prevent Mystique from killing Bolivar Trask, an evil military scientist, whose murder had led to the creation of robots meant to slaughter humans and mutants.

name: Rise of the Planet of the Apes
title: 2011 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 45m
description: Caesar, a chimpanzee, has been with Will ever since he was born, and, with a new drug, he can think and react like humans. When Caesar finds himself subjected to injustice, he decides to revolt.

name: Prometheus
title: 2012 ‧ Sci-fi/Horror ‧ 2h 4m
description: After a clue to mankind's origins is discovered, explorers are sent to the darkest corner of the universe. Their different expectations take a toll on them when they find something unimaginable.

name: Alien: Resurrection
title: 1997 ‧ Horror/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 49m
description: Ripley 8, a human-alien hybrid clone, is aboard a vessel, Auriga, along with space pirates. However, when aliens invade Auriga, Ripley does her best to prevent them from reaching and destroying Earth.

name: The Grey
title: 2011 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 57m
description: When a plane carrying oil workers crashes in Alaska's wilderness, seven of them survive. John, a wolf hunter, leads them through the heavy snow as they are chased and attacked by relentless wolves.

name: The Descent
title: 2005 ‧ Horror/Adventure ‧ 1h 39m
description: A group of friends set out on an expedition to a cave. Their adventure turns into a nightmare when they get trapped inside the cave and are pursued by bloodthirsty predators.

name: The Mist
title: 2007 ‧ Horror/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 6m
description: David and his son are trapped in a supermarket along with some other townsfolk, when suddenly a mist engulfs the entire city, bringing along bloodthirsty creatures that devour anyone in their path.

name: Slither
title: 2006 ‧ Horror/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 35m
description: When an extraterrestrial parasite infects the citizens of a town with the intent of devouring all life forms on Earth, it is up to the town sheriff and a local woman to put an end to the monster.

name: Jurassic World
title: 2015 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 4m
description: A theme park showcasing genetically-engineered dinosaurs turns into a nightmare for its tourists when one of the dinosaurs escapes its enclosure. An ex-military animal expert steps up to save the day.

name: The Lost World: Jurassic Park
title: 1997 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 9m
description: Two teams are appointed to find about the existence of dinosaurs who survived secretly. One of the leaders is aware of a second island apart from Isla Nublar that led to the failure of Jurassic Park.

name: Jurassic Park III
title: 2001 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 1h 32m
description: Dr Alan Grant struggles to get funding together for his dinosaur research. However, a wealthy couple offers to give him money in return for a tour of a deadly island.

name: Star Trek
title: 2009 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 2h 7m
description: James Kirk, a brash young man, and Spock, an alien with human and Vulcan blood, join the crew of the USS Enterprise to combat Nero, a member of the Romulan race who wants to destroy multiple planets.

name: Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home
title: 1986 ‧ Family/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 59m
description: Admiral Kirk wants to save planet Earth from an alien probe. He goes back in time with his crew to retrieve the extinct humpback whales which in return will help to save the planet.

name: Black Panther
title: 2018 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 14m
description: After his father's death, T'Challa returns home to Wakanda to inherit his throne. However, a powerful enemy related to his family threatens to attack his nation.

name: Ant-Man and the Wasp
title: 2018 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 1h 58m
description: Despite being under house arrest, Scott Lang, along with the Wasp, sets out to help Dr Hank Pym to enter the quantum realm as they face new enemies along the way.

name: Godzilla: King of the Monsters
title: 2019 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 2h 12m
description: A legendary monster named King Ghidorah awakens Rodan, as well as other titans, to destroy the world. To defeat them, the crypto-zoological organisation Monarch must rely on the almighty Godzilla.

name: Godzilla vs. Kong
title: 2021 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 53m
description: King Kong is transported out of his containment zone after Godzilla resurfaces and creates mayhem. Humans need his help to reach Hollow Earth and find a way to subdue the king of the monsters.

name: Independence Day
title: 1996 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 2h 25m
description: An alien race destroys major cities of the world with their advanced weaponry. However, a geek, a pilot, the US President and a group of ragtag survivors unite to save mankind from annihilation.

name: Guardians of the Galaxy
title: 2014 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 2m
description: A bunch of skilled criminals led by brash adventurer Peter Quill join hands to fight a villain named Ronan the Accuser who wants to control the universe with the help of a mystical orb.

name: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3
title: 2023 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 29m
description: Still reeling from the loss of Gamora, Peter Quill must rally his team to defend the universe and protect one of their own. If the mission is not completely successful, it could possibly lead to the end of the Guardians as we know them.

name: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom
title: 2018 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 9m
description: After a volcano eruption proves to be a threat for the dinosaurs, Owen and Claire reach the defunct Jurassic World, a theme park, to save the animals from extinction.

name: Transformers
title: 2007 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 2h 24m
description: Autobots and Decepticons, races from outer space, engage in a humongous and fierce battle on planet Earth. The Autobots enlist the help of a teenager, Sam, to win the battle against the Decepticons.

name: Predator
title: 1987 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 47m
description: Dutch and his team are out on a mission to rescue a group of hostages in Central America. There, they discover that they are being targeted by an extraterrestrial warrior.

name: Giri/Haji
title: 2019 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Translating to Duty/Shame and set in both Tokyo and London, "Giri/Haji" is a thriller about a Tokyo detective named Kenzo Mori, scouring the London underworld to find his allegedly deceased brother, Yuto. Yuto was accused of brutally murdering the nephew of a yakuza member, which could lead to the onset of a gang war. Kenzo's investigation into the disappearance lures him into dangerous elements of the corrupt underworld of London's criminal circuit. Starring an international ensemble cast, the series originally aired on BBC2.

name: Tokyo Vice
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Jake Adelstein, an American journalist, plugs into the Tokyo Vice police squad and descends into the neon underbelly of Tokyo.

name: Blood of Zeus
title: 2020 ‧ Action ‧ 2 seasons
description: Chronicles the illegitimate son of Zeus, a young man tasked with saving heaven and earth despite the interference of a vengeful goddess and her monstrous forces.

name: Blue Eye Samurai
title: 2023 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: A master of the sword lives life in disguise while seeking revenge in Edo-period Japan.

name: Afro Samurai
title: 2007 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: In a feudal Japan of the future, a young warrior sets out to avenge the murder of his father, encountering life-altering lessons in brutality, love, betrayal and loss along his journey.

name: Million Yen Women
title: 2017 ‧ 1 season
description: Five beautiful but mysterious women move in with unsuccessful novelist Shin, who manages their odd household in exchange for a tidy monthly sum.

name: Burn the House Down
title: 2023 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: To uncover the truth about the fire that ruined her family thirteen years ago, Anzu decides to go undercover as a housekeeper for the icy mistress of the wealthy and powerful Mitarai home.

name: Our Flag Means Death
title: 2022 ‧ Adventure ‧ 2 seasons
description: Stede Bonnet, an unhappy aristocrat, abandons his family and comfortable life to become a pirate despite his lack of experience in crime and at sea.

name: The Last Kingdom
title: 2015 ‧ Drama ‧ 5 seasons
description: Uhtred, the son of a nobleman, is captured and raised by Danes. Once he grows up, he has to choose whom he will protect, the land where he grew up or the people who raised him as their own.

name: Band of Brothers
title: 2001 ‧ History ‧ 1 season
description: The story of Easy Company, 506th Regiment of the 101st Airborne Division from 1942 to the end of World War II. A collection of fifty portraits illustrated by archive footage and recounted in voice.

name: The Pacific
title: 2010 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Three Marines from different regiments face difficult situations and must struggle to survive during America's battle with the Japanese in the Pacific during World War II.

name: Generation Kill
title: 2008 ‧ War ‧ 1 season
description: Evan 'Scribe' Wright is a journalist for The Rolling Stones. He persuades the commander to recruit him into the 1st Reconnaissance Battalion, so he may document the assault on Baghdad.

name: Foundation
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: A complex saga of humans scattered on planets throughout the galaxy all living under the rule of the Galactic Empire. Dr Hari Seldon and his loyal followers attempt to preserve their culture as the galaxy collapses around them.

name: Miss Scarlet and the Duke
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 4 seasons
description: Eliza Scarlet teams up with a male partner to direct her father's detective agency and solve crimes in Victorian England.

name: Sister Boniface Mysteries
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: Sister Boniface of Saint Vincent's Convent helps the police solve various crimes in the local village, which is called Great Slaughter because it is known for its unexpectedly large body count, whilst also making wine and driving her vespa.

name: Frank Herbert's Dune
title: 2000 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 1 season
description: Frank Herbert's intricate epic traces a galactic feud between two royal houses.

name: Frank Herbert's Children of Dune
title: 2003 ‧ Adventure ‧ 1 season
description: On the desert planet of Dune, the emperor's young son Leto Atreides and daughter Ghanima face the prospect of a disastrous civil war on Arrakis and chaos on a galactic scale.

name: The Book of Boba Fett
title: 2021 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: On the sands of Tatooine, bounty hunter Boba Fett and mercenary Fennec Shand navigate the Galaxy's underworld and fight for Jabba the Hutt's old territory.

name: Universal Soldier
title: 1992 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 42m
description: Soldiers Luc and Andrew's dead bodies are stored for a programme that can resurrect the deceased and turn them into killing machines. Complications arise when they start having memories of the past.

name: Lionheart
title: 1990 ‧ Action/Sport ‧ 1h 45m
description: A foreign legion deserter arrives in the US after learning that his brother has been murdered and his family is in financial distress. He participates in underground street fights to support them.

name: Double Impact
title: 1991 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 50m
description: The story revolves around twins who separate during childhood when their parents get killed by a crime boss. Years later, they join forces to exact revenge on the people who took their parents' lives.

name: American Ninja
title: 1985 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 1h 35m
description: Joe Armstrong, an amnesiac man, is ordered to serve in the US Army as an alternative to a prison sentence. His life changes when he fights off a group of ninjas single-handedly at his base.

name: Missing in Action
title: 1984 ‧ Action/War ‧ 1h 41m
description: A military officer escapes from a Vietnamese POW camp. However, he realises that several American troops are still being held captive in Vietnam, forcing him to plot a strategy to liberate them.

name: Cobra
title: 1986 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 27m
description: A gang of neo-fascist thugs break into people's homes and kill them at random. Cobretti is brought on to end these activities, which leads to a battle between the thugs and Cobretti.

name: Commando
title: 1985 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 30m
description: Ex-black ops commando John's daughter Jenny is kidnapped by a band of revenge-seeking thugs. With only a few hours to find and rescue his child, this one-man army sets out on an explosive mission.

name: The Enforcer
title: 1995 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 45m
description: Kung Wei, a police officer, infiltrates a terrorist gang to understand their plan. Things go wrong during his mission and he ends up jeopardizing his son's life.

name: Bloodfist II
title: 1990 ‧ Action/Sport ‧ 1h 39m
description: The world kickboxing champion (Don "The Dragon" Wilson) retreats to Manila, lands in a mess and fights his way out.

name: Universal Soldier: The Return
title: 1999 ‧ Action/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 23m
description: Luc, a retired Universal Soldier, works as a technical advisor to perfect the Universal Soldier program. When the computer programme running the soldiers goes rogue, Luc is tasked with stopping it.

name: Missing in Action 2: The Beginning
title: 1985 ‧ Action/War ‧ 1h 40m
description: Braddock is captured and finds himself at a POW camp run by a sadistic colonel in league with the drug lords. Braddock must find a way to escape and help the other POWs before it is too late.

name: Braddock: Missing in Action III
title: 1988 ‧ Action/War ‧ 1h 43m
description: James Braddock returns to Vietnam, 12 years after the end of the war, to rescue his thought-dead Vietnamese wife and son, and a group of orphans held in a prison camp by a sadistic Vietnamese general.

name: The Passage
title: 2019 ‧ Action/Drama ‧ 2h 30m
description: In 1967 and during the Six-Day War, Nour, a war commander, leads his soldiers through thick and thin with the support of his wife.

name: Arrest Letter
title: 2017 ‧ Action/Thriller
description: A man joins a terrorist organisation to fight a holy war. However, when his brother, who wants to become a part of the movement, is killed, he turns his back towards his group and seeks revenge.

name: Sons of Rizk 2
title: 2019 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 8m
description: Rizk's sons try to avoid the path of crime and theft as they agreed, but a sudden event entangles them with a group of dangerous criminals, which changes their lives.

name: Chaos
title: 2007 ‧ Drama/Melodrama ‧ 2h 4m
description: Hatem, a police officer, misuses his designation to make personal gains. He harasses Nour, an innocent girl, when she refuses to agree to his demands.

name: Five Nights at Freddy's
title: 2023 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 1h 50m
description: A troubled security guard begins working at Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria. While spending his first night on the job, he realizes the late shift at Freddy's won't be so easy to make it through.

name: Seven Samurai
title: 1954 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 3h 27m
description: A veteran samurai gathers six of his men to protect a village from the cruel bandits. As the samurais teach the natives how to defend themselves, the village is attacked by a group of 40 bandits.

name: Silent Hill
title: 2006 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 2h 7m
description: Rose and her daughter, Sharon, leave their house to go to Silent Hill. On their way Rose meets with an accident knocking her unconscious and when she awakes, Sharon is missing.

name: High and Low
title: 1963 ‧ Thriller/Crime ‧ 2h 23m
description: Gondo, a wealthy executive, desires to buy a shoe company. However, he faces challenges when his driver's son gets kidnapped and he is forced to pay a huge ransom in order to save him.

name: 13 Assassins
title: 2010 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 21m
description: Lord Naritsugu Matsudaira is being ruthless towards his own people in Japan. To stop him, a team of 13 warriors band together although it means losing their lives.

name: Dracula Untold
title: 2014 ‧ Action/Horror ‧ 1h 32m
description: Vlad the Impaler, a Transylvanian prince, turns himself into a vampire to protect his family and the kingdom from the invading Turkish forces.

name: The Lost Boys
title: 1987 ‧ Horror/Comedy ‧ 1h 37m
description: Lucy along with her two sons, Michael and Sam moves to a small town in California. Soon, the two boys are sucked into the mysterious and dangerous world of bikers, vampires and vampire hunters.

name: Robin Hood: Men in Tights
title: 1993 ‧ Comedy/Adventure ‧ 1h 44m
description: After Prince John assumes control over England, he captures Robin Hood's family home. Chaos ensues when Robin does his best to retrieve his land.

name: Frankenstein
title: 1931 ‧ Horror/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 11m
description: A deranged scientist becomes obsessed with assembling a living being out of parts of several exhumed corpses. However, he accidentally uses the brain of a madman.

name: The Mummy
title: 1932 ‧ Horror/Fantasy ‧ 1h 13m
description: An Egyptian mummy discovered in an archaeological expedition returns to life to stalk the reincarnation of his lost love.

name: Hellbound: Hellraiser II
title: 1988 ‧ Horror/Drama ‧ 1h 39m
description: A psychiatric prison in-charge unleashes a bunch of pain-seeking demons while meddling with a satanic puzzle cube. As the demons begin to harass his daughter, she must find a way to solve the puzzle.

name: Only Lovers Left Alive
title: 2013 ‧ Romance/Horror ‧ 2h 3m
description: Adam, a vampire, is depressed after seeing society plummet to the bottom. Eve, his lover of centuries past, comes to his rescue. But their relationship is tested with the arrival of Ava, Eve's sister.

name: Monster
title: 2023 ‧ Thriller/Drama ‧ 2h 7m
description: A single mother demands answers from a school teacher when her son begins acting strangely. A fight at school causes even more trouble.

name: Schindler's List
title: 1993 ‧ War/Drama ‧ 3h 15m
description: Oscar Schindler, a successful and narcissistic German businessman, slowly starts worrying about the safety of his Jewish workforce after witnessing their persecution in Poland during World War II.

name: In the Mood for Love
title: 2000 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 38m
description: In 1962, journalist Chow Mo-wan (Tony Leung Chiu Wai) and his wife move into a Hong Kong apartment, but Chow's spouse is often away on business. Before long, the lonely Chow makes the acquaintance of the alluring Su Li-zhen (Maggie Cheung Man-yuk), whose own significant other also seems preoccupied with work. As the two friends realize their respective partners are cheating on them, they begin to fall for one another; however, neither wants to stoop to the level of the unfaithful spouses.

name: Little Miss Sunshine
title: 2006 ‧ Comedy/Drama ‧ 1h 41m
description: A family decides to travel across the country when their daughter wants to participate in a beauty pageant, unaware of the surprises the journey has in store for them.

name: The Crush
title: 2010 ‧ Comedy/Romance ‧ 15 mins
description: Ardal Travis is in love. There's just one problem. He's an 8-year old schoolboy and the object of his affection is his second class teacher, Miss Purdy.

name: The Confession
title: 2010 ‧ Thriller/Drama ‧ 26 mins
description: With a clear conscience, a man is nearly ready for his first confession, then he and a friend play a prank that turns tragic.

name: New Boy
title: 2007 ‧ Drama/Short ‧ 11 mins
description: Based on a short story by Roddy Doyle, this poignant and comedic short film deftly captures the experience of being the new boy in school through the eyes of Joseph, a nine-year-old African boy.

name: The Silent Child
title: 2017 ‧ Thriller/Drama ‧ 20 mins
description: Joanne, a social worker, teaches sign language to a four-year-old Libby, who has a hearing disability. However, Libby's family is ignorant of her needs and instead force her to learn lip-reading.

name: Fantastic Mr. Fox
title: 2009 ‧ Family/Comedy ‧ 1h 27m
description: Mr Fox, a family man, goes back to his ways of stealing, unable to resist his animal instincts. However, he finds himself trapped when three farmers decide to kill him and his kind.

name: Zero
title: 2010 ‧ Drama/Animation ‧ 13 mins
description: Born into a world that judges people by their number, Zero faces constant oppression and prejudice. Eventually, he discovers that happiness can be achieved with some determination and courage.

name: Rescue Dawn
title: 2006 ‧ War/Action ‧ 2h 6m
description: Following a crash during the Vietnam War, fighter pilot Dieter gets caught by peasants. In captivity, he hatches and executes an escape plan with five deranged prisoners only to face bigger hurdles.

name: Exit Through the Gift Shop
title: 2010 ‧ Comedy/Crime ‧ 1h 27m
description: Tells the tale of Thierry Guetta, a French immigrant in Los Angeles, and his undying love for street art.

name: WALL-E
title: 2008 ‧ Family/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 38m
description: A robot who is responsible for cleaning a waste-covered Earth meets another robot and falls in love with her. Together, they set out on a journey that will alter the fate of mankind.

name: 27 Dresses
title: 2008 ‧ Comedy/Romance ‧ 1h 51m
description: After serving as a bridesmaid 27 times, Jane is shocked when her younger sister announces her engagement to the man she loves. Meanwhile, she also meets a cynical journalist who has a hidden agenda.

name: The Devil Wears Prada
title: 2006 ‧ Comedy/Drama ‧ 1h 49m
description: With an aspiration to become a journalist, Andy, a young graduate, travels to New York. She starts working as an assistant to one of the city's biggest magazine editors, the cynical Miranda Priestly.

name: The Proposal
title: 2009 ‧ Comedy/Romance ‧ 1h 48m
description: In order to avoid deportation to Canada, Margaret, the editor of a publishing firm, convinces her assistant Andrew to marry her. However, a trip to Andrew's hometown leads to unexpected consequences.

name: Thirteen Lives
title: 2022 ‧ Thriller/Action ‧ 2h 27m
description: A rescue mission is assembled in Thailand where a group of young boys and their soccer coach are trapped in a system of underground caves that are flooding.

name: The Florida Project
title: 2017 ‧ Drama/Indie film ‧ 1h 51m
description: Moonee, a six-year-old girl, lives with her mother near Disneyland and spends the summer pranking and stealing from tourists while her mother struggles to make ends meet.

name: The Magnificent Seven
title: 2016 ‧ Western/Action ‧ 2h 12m
description: Sam Chisolm, a warrant officer, is requested by the citizens of the town of Rose Creek to apprehend Bartholomew Bogue, a corrupt industrialist, and his ruthless gang who are terrorising them.

name: Student Seduction
title: 2003 ‧ Thriller/Drama ‧ 2 hours
description: A schoolteacher who is accused of sexually assaulting one of her students must prove that she was the victim of an assault and not the student.

name: Milk
title: 2017 ‧ Drama ‧ 15 mins
description: To celebrate her daughter's birthday, Ewa prepares a party at their lake house. However, she is not prepared for Julia, the daughter, to bring her boyfriend whom she just cannot stand.

name: First Response
title: 2015 ‧ Thriller/Action ‧ 1h 29m
description: After a failed robbery attempt, a gunman hijacks an ambulance and forces Camilla, a paramedic, to drive it. Camilla, who is held at gunpoint, must do the right thing before it's too late.

name: Love Like the Falling Petals
title: 2022 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 2h 8m
description: Photographer Haruto falls head over heels for his hair stylist, Misaki. When he finally asks her out, it seems to be happily ever after for the young couple, until Misaki develops a rare disease that causes her to age rapidly before their eyes.

name: Elisa & Marcela
title: 2019 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 58m
description: In the mid-1880s in Spain, Elisa and Marcela, two classmates, fall head over heels in love with each other. Tired of dealing with the secret, Elisa decides to adopt a man's identity to marry Marcela.

name: Decision to Leave
title: 2022 ‧ Romance/Mystery ‧ 2h 18m
description: A detective investigating a man's death in the mountains ends up meeting and developing feelings for the dead man's mysterious wife in the course of his dogged sleuthing.

name: You Can Live Forever
title: 2022 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 36m
description: When lesbian teen Jaime is sent to live in a Jehovah's Witness community, she falls hard for a devout girl and the two embark on an intense affair with consequences that reshape their lives.

name: A Perfect Ending
title: 2012 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 54m
description: Rebecca reveals her unusual secret to an escort and tries to find her true self.

name: Portrait of a Lady on Fire
title: 2019 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 2h 1m
description: Marianne, a female painter, is commissioned to paint a portrait of Heloise, an aristocratic woman, in a wedding dress. They soon fall in love with each other but cannot unite.

name: Below Her Mouth
title: 2016 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 34m
description: Jasmine is a successful fashion editor living with her fiance. On a night out in the city with her best friend, she meets Dallas, a roofer recently out of a relationship. Surprised by the confidence with which Dallas pursues her, Jasmine turns Dallas down but can't get her out of her head. When Jasmine finally succumbs, the two women embark on a steamy affair that forces them both to re-evaluate their lives.

name: Payback
title: 1999 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 40m
description: Porter is betrayed by his friend and wife after a successful robbery. With the help of a few other criminal masterminds, he sets out on a dangerous venture to seek revenge.

name: Non-Stop
title: 2014 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 30m
description: A US air marshal receives threatening messages demanding that his airline transfer 150 million dollars to an offshore account, in the absence of which the passengers of his flight will be killed.

name: The Weeknd: Live at SoFi Stadium
title: 2023 ‧ Musical/Musical genre ‧ 1h 37m
description: The Weeknd brings fans up-close with a special, intimate concert presented at SoFi Stadium in Los Angeles during the first U.S. leg of his "After Hours Til Dawn Tour," captured cinematically as he performs hits from his studio albums.

name: Sylvie's Love
title: 2020 ‧ Romance/Drama ‧ 1h 54m
description: Sylvie has a summer romance with a saxophonist who takes a summer job at her father's record store in Harlem; when they reconnect years later, they discover that their feelings for each other have not faded with the years.

name: La chimera
title: 2023 ‧ Adventure/Comedy ‧ 2h 13m
description: Everyone has their own Chimera, something they try to achieve but can never find. For Arthur, the Chimera is the woman he lost, Beniamina.

name: Sniper
title: 1993 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 38m
description: US Marine sniper Thomas Scott is accompanied with marksman, Richard Miller in the Panamanian forest. There, they must eliminate a rebel leader using sniper techniques and skills.

name: Tears of the Sun
title: 2003 ‧ Action/War ‧ 2h 22m
description: A special operation commander, along with his troop, sets off to rescue Dr Lena from the jungles of Nigeria. However, Dr Lena agrees to join them only if they agree to rescue 70 other refugees too.

name: Enemy at the Gates
title: 2001 ‧ War/Action ‧ 2h 11m
description: Russian sniper Vasily Zaytsev bumps off Nazi German soldiers one by one during the Battle of Stalingrad in 1942-1943. German Major Konig is ordered to slay Vasily to restore Adolf Hitler's honour.

name: Destined With You
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: A lawyer bound by a centuries-old curse becomes entangled with a civil servant who holds the key to his freedom.

name: Exhuma
title: 2024 ‧ Horror/Mystery ‧ 2h 14m
description: The process of excavating an ominous grave unleashes long hidden secrets and dreadful consequences buried underneath.

name: Bulgasal: Immortal Souls
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: An immortal man's life becomes intertwined with that of a woman who lives with a cycle of death and reincarnation.

name: The Uncanny Counter
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Demon hunters pose as workers in a noodle shop in an effort to catch evil spirits hoping to find eternal life.

name: Abyss
title: 2019 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: After meeting an untimely demise in separate incidents, Cha Min and Go Se-yeon discover they've come back to life in new bodies they don't recognize.

name: Doom at Your Service
title: 2021 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: A woman who lost her parents in early age is diagnosed with a brain tumour, forcing her to have less than 100 days to live. As she prays for the destruction of the world, the destruction himself comes to her and live with her for the last 100 days.

name: Alchemy of Souls
title: 2022 ‧ Romance ‧ 2 seasons
description: A powerful sorceress in a blind woman's body encounters a man from a prestigious family, who wants her help to change his destiny.

name: My Demon
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: Heiress Do Do Hee is an adversary to many, and Jung Koo Won is a powerful entity; when Jung Koo Won loses his powers, he must collaborate with Do Do Hee to regain them, and sparks fly between them as they embark on their journey.

name: A Korean Odyssey
title: 2017 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Son Oh-gong, a mythical creature, gets imprisoned due to his useless antics. However, he tries to take advantage of Seon-mi, a girl with the third eye, to regain his immortality.

name: The Kidnapping Day
title: 2023 ‧ Thriller ‧ 1 season
description: In dire need of money to pay for his daughter's hospital bills, Myeong-jun decides to kidnap a girl named Ro-hee in exchange for a ransom from her rich parents.

name: Behind Your Touch
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: A psychic veterinarian and a detective join forces to crack small-town cases, but their skills are tested as they unravel a mystery involving a serial killer.

name: A Time Called You
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: A young woman mourns the death of her boyfriend. As a result, she is inexplicably transported back in time in the body of a high school student. There she meets a student who looks confusingly like the deceased.

name: Still 17
title: 2018 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: Woo Seo Ri is a violinist who wakes up from her coma after 17 years. She adjusts to her new surroundings and suddenly meets Gong Woo Jin, a man whose trauma makes him reluctant to fall in love.

name: The King's Affection
title: 2021 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: During the Joseon Dynasty, the Crown Princess Consort gives birth to twins but sends the girl away to spare her life. Years later, the twin son dies in an accident and his sister must assume his identity and throne, all while hiding her true self.

name: See You in My 19th Life
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: Ban Ji-eum, who can remember all her past lives, sets out to reconnect with a lost love from her 18th life, which was cut tragically short.

name: BITCH X RICH
title: 2023 ‧ Thriller ‧ 1 season
description: Kim Hye In has to transfer to Cheongdam International High School after witnessing a murder. She crosses paths with Baek Je Na, a bully who happens to be connected to the case.

name: Heartbeat
title: 2023 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: When fate brings a half-human, half-vampire man and a cold-hearted woman together, they have to learn to care for each other.

name: School 2017
title: 2017 ‧ Romance ‧ 1 season
description: A group of students, who go through several ups and downs, try to cope with their personal problems as well as deal with a corrupt system at school.

name: Presumed Innocent
title: 2024 ‧ Thriller ‧ 1 season
description: A horrific murder upends the Chicago prosecuting attorney's office when one of its own is suspected of the crime, leaving the accused fighting to keep his family together.

name: The Expanse
title: 2015 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 6 seasons
description: Josephus Miller, an interstellar police detective, is assigned to find a missing woman, who turns out to be a part of a large conspiracy that threatens humanity.

name: Silo
title: 2023 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: In a ruined and toxic future, a community exists in a giant underground silo that plunges hundreds of stories deep; there, people live in a society full of regulations they believe are meant to protect them.

name: Severance
title: 2022 ‧ Thriller ‧ 1 season
description: Mark leads a team of office workers whose memories have been surgically divided between their work and personal lives; when a mysterious colleague appears outside of work, it begins a journey to discover the truth about their jobs.

name: Biohackers
title: 2020 ‧ Thriller ‧ 2 seasons
description: A medical student enters a top German university on a secret mission to uncover a conspiracy linking a family tragedy to a biology professor.

name: Warrior
title: 2019 ‧ Action ‧ 3 seasons
description: In San Francisco, California, Ah Sahm, a martial arts prodigy from China, leads a colourful life as he becomes a hatchet man for a powerful tong.

name: Marco Polo
title: 2014 ‧ History ‧ 2 seasons
description: Venetian merchant and adventurer Marco Polo journeys across Europe and Asia and lands up as a prisoner in the palace of Kublai Khan, a 13th century Mongolian emperor.

name: Raised by Wolves
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Raised by Wolves is an American science fiction drama television series created by Aaron Guzikowski that premiered on HBO Max on September 3, 2020. The first two episodes were directed by Ridley Scott, who also serves as an executive producer for the show.

name: Battlestar Galactica
title: 2004 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 4 seasons
description: A group of humans aboard a battleship, Battlestar Galactica, are forced to abandon their planet after being attacked by Cylons. They try to evade the Cylons while searching for their true home, Earth.

name: The Rain
title: 2018 ‧ Thriller ‧ 3 seasons
description: The world as we know it has come to an end, due to a rain-carried virus that wiped out nearly everybody in Scandinavia. Six years after that event, two Danish siblings emerge from the safety of the bunker where they have been staying. After discovering all remnants of civilization gone, they join a group of fellow young survivors, and together they head out on a danger-filled quest throughout the abandoned land in search of signs of life. The survivors think they have been set free from societal rules of the past, but they quickly find that even in a post-apocalyptic world there is love, jealousy and other coming-of-age dilemmas that young people have always faced.

name: Falling Skies
title: 2011 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 5 seasons
description: Global invasion of an alien attack destroys a huge number of human population within a few days, giving rise to Second Massachusetts, a group formed by the survivors who band together to fight back.

name: The Climb
title: 2023 ‧ Reality ‧ 1 season
description: The Climb is an 8-episode reality TV series that pits 10 amateur climbers against each other in multiple climbing scenarios and styles. The winner receives $100,000 USD and a $100,000 USD sponsorship from outdoor gear producer, prAna.

name: Away
title: 2020 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Emma Green embarks on a treacherous mission to Mars in command of an international crew, leaving behind her husband and teenage daughter.

name: Lost in Space
title: 2018 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 3 seasons
description: Due to unforeseeable circumstances, the Robinsons, a family of space colonists, crash-land on an unknown planet. Now, they must fight for survival and escape, despite the dangers surrounding them.

name: Doctor Who
title: 2005 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 13 seasons
description: The Doctor, an extraterrestrial being, travels across time and space through a unique device called TARDIS. It travels to Earth and befriends humans who help it in its exploits.

name: Doctor Who Confidential
title: 2005 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 6 seasons
description: The show goes behind the scenes on the hit series, Doctor Who, reflecting on the show's past as well as embracing its future too.

name: Torchwood
title: 2006 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 4 seasons
description: A team of alien hunters sets up the Torchwood Institute to deal with incidents involving extraterrestrials.

name: Bosch: Legacy
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Harry Bosch embarks on the next chapter of his career and finds himself working with onetime enemy, Honey Chandler.

name: Longmire
title: 2012 ‧ Western ‧ 6 seasons
description: After his wife's death, Walt Longmire, a county sheriff, returns to work. With the help of his friends, he manages to investigate several dangerous crimes.

name: Bosch
title: 2014 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: Harry Bosch, a detective working with the Los Angeles Police Department, is accused of murdering a serial killer. At that time, he is simultaneously investigating the murder of a young boy.

name: Curb Your Enthusiasm
title: 2000 ‧ Sitcom ‧ 12 seasons
description: Larry David, a famous television writer and producer, gets into various misadventures with his friends and celebrity colleagues in Los Angeles.

name: Queen of the South
title: 2016 ‧ Drama ‧ 5 seasons
description: Teresa flees to the United States after her drug-peddling boyfriend is murdered by a cartel boss. There, she sets out to become a drug lord and vows to avenge her lover's death.

name: Person of Interest
title: 2011 ‧ Sci-fi ‧ 5 seasons
description: Harold Finch teams up with an ex-CIA agent to use the Machine to prevent crimes before they are committed. However, they are pursued by the government and people who are interested in the Machine .

name: The Undoing
title: 2020 ‧ 1 season
description: Grace, a therapist who is looking forward to publishing her first novel, comes across some startling revelations and must act fast to protect her and her son.

name: Fargo
title: 2014 ‧ Drama ‧ 5 seasons
description: A disparate set of characters deal with a plethora of crimes in different time periods. The only thing they share in common is their connection to the Midwest, USA.

name: Shades of Blue
title: 2016 ‧ 3 seasons
description: Jennifer Lopez stars as New York detective Harlee Santos, a single mother who runs with a group of dirty cops, taking her cut of the bribes and protection money to give her bright and promising daughter the best life possible and a leg up for a better future. However, all good things must come to an end and she is caught by the FBI, which forces her to turn informant on her cop family. Harlee struggles to walk a line between loyalty, honour and betrayal, all the while working to keep everything together for her daughter.

name: Vinyl
title: 2016 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Richie Finestra, a shrewd record executive from New York, tries to promote American Century, his music label, amidst the changing music scene in the 1970s.

name: Blindspot
title: 2015 ‧ Drama ‧ 5 seasons
description: The FBI finds a mysterious tattooed woman in Times Square with no memory of her identity. As she tries to uncover her past, her tattoos are found to contain clues alluding to a criminal conspiracy.

name: Homeland
title: 2011 ‧ Drama ‧ 8 seasons
description: CIA operative Carrie Mathison is on the lookout for an American prisoner who may have joined forces with Al-Qaeda. Released from hostage after eight years, Marine Nicholas Brody becomes her suspect.

name: Mad Men
title: 2007 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: Donald Draper, the creative director at Sterling Cooper in New York, tries to maintain a balance between his exceptional professional life and wavering personal life in the 1960s.

name: Ray Donovan
title: 2013 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: Ray Donovan works as a mediator for a law firm that handles celebrities and wealthy clients. While Ray is an expert in solving other people's problems, he has no control over his personal issues.

name: Sons of Anarchy
title: 2008 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: Jax Teller, a man in his early 30s, struggles to find a balance in his life between being a new dad and his involvement in a motorcycle gang.

name: Snatch
title: 2017 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: A group of hustlers accidentally discover a truck-load of stolen gold. Once they lay their hands on the treasure, they get entangled in the world of crime.

name: Family Law
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: A suspended lawyer and recovering alcoholic, Abby, is forced to work at her estranged father's law firm among other members of her dysfunctional family as she tries to put her life back together.

name: Law & Order: Special Victims Unit
title: 1999 ‧ Drama ‧ 25 seasons
description: A group of specially trained detectives from the NYPD form a group known as the Special Victims Unit where they try to solve crimes related to sexual assault and harassment.

name: Law & Order
title: 1990 ‧ Drama ‧ 23 seasons
description: Police officers investigate a series of brutal crimes and try to apprehend the culprits. They provide necessary evidence in order to help prosecutors bring justice in the court of law.

name: Law & Order: Criminal Intent
title: 2001 ‧ Drama ‧ 10 seasons
description: Detectives Goren, Alexandra, Logan and Megan form the smartest team in the department. Together, they solve the most baffling cases while studying the psychological aspects of crime and criminals.

title: 2018 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: Policemen, paramedics and firefighters put themselves in dangerous situations to save people's lives. Meanwhile, they also have to deal with their personal problems.

name: The Protector
title: 2011 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Gloria Sheppard is an intuitive LAPD homicide detective who juggles her demanding personal and professional lives while raising two sons with the help of her troubled younger brother, Davey. Helping Gloria with her police work are her partner, Michelle Dulcett, and her boss, Lt. Felix Valdez.

name: Justice
title: 2006 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Ron Trott, an accomplished lawyer, who runs one of the most powerful law firms in Los Angeles, works ruthlessly with a team of professionals to win any case that is handed to him.

name: Major Crimes
title: 2012 ‧ Drama ‧ 6 seasons
description: Captain Sharon Raydor leads the Major Crimes division in Los Angeles. She and the team enforce the law amidst internal friction and challenging cases.

name: Castle
title: 2009 ‧ Drama ‧ 8 seasons
description: When a psychopath commits murders based on novelist Castle's books, Detective Beckett seeks his help to solve the case. He decides to work with her and uses his experiences as research for his novels.

name: Burn Notice
title: 2007 ‧ Drama ‧ 7 seasons
description: US spy Michael Weston suddenly finds himself 'burned'-discredited without any form of procedure. Since no one will really help him, he survives by doing impossible jobs for desperate people in Miami.

name: The Staircase
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Author Michael Peterson's life turns upside down when he becomes the prime suspect in the death of his wife, Kathleen. Soon, his ordeal turns into a harrowing tale of never-ending court trials.

name: The Killing
title: 2011 ‧ Drama ‧ 4 seasons
description: After the brutal murder of Rosie Larsen, a 17-year-old, occurs, the detectives leave no stone unturned to find the killer. They discover certain clues that lead them to Seattle.

name: Broadchurch
title: 2013 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: When the corpse of an 11-year-old British boy, Danny Latimer, is found bloodied and dirty on an idyllic beach, a small Dorset community becomes the focus of a police investigation and media madness. Out-of-town Detective Inspector Alec Hardy gets the point position over Detective Sgt. Ellie Miller -- who feels the job should have been hers. Now she must engage in an efficient working relationship with taciturn Hardy. Slowly, more members of the community of Broadchurch are drawn into the investigation, with a telephone engineer drawing great attention when he admits to a special connection to the case. While dealing with so much unwelcome attention, Danny's family tries to cope with its grief. When a suspect is named and charged, the ensuing trial sees the defendant promising to expose more of the townspeople's secrets.

name: Big Little Lies
title: 2017 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Madeline, Celeste and Jane are a trio of wealthy young women in Monterey, California. Their lives are shattered when a murder takes place in their idyllic town, unravelling a can of worms.

name: The Detectives
title: 2018 ‧ Drama ‧ 3 seasons
description: "The Detectives" brings gripping and factual work of detectives to life. Every hourlong episode features a different detective as he relives his most challenging investigation and reflects on the impact it had in relation to Canadian law enforcement and the Canadian way of life. Intimate and raw interviews are laid bare for all to see in this meticulously crafted documentary. Such investigations include a man going missing after meeting someone from an online dating site, a 3-year-old witness to a murder in his home, a bomb threat and a killer threatening to strike again, and the disappearance of a young woman, among others.

name: The Gilded Age
title: 2022 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Marian Brook, a rural girl, moves to New York after her father's death. However, things get complicated when she must assimilate into the clan of a railroad tycoon.

name: Alias Grace
title: 2017 ‧ Drama ‧ 1 season
description: Grace, an Irish immigrant in Canada, is convicted of the murder of her employer. However, things take a different turn when a psychiatrist arrives to analyse her mental state.

name: Only Murders in the Building
title: 2021 ‧ Mystery ‧ 3 seasons
description: Three strangers share an obsession with true crime and suddenly find themselves wrapped up in one. When a grisly death occurs inside their exclusive Upper West Side apartment building, the trio suspects murder and employs their precise knowledge of true crime to investigate the truth. Perhaps even more explosive are the lies they tell one another. Soon, the endangered trio comes to realize a killer might be living among them as they race to decipher the mounting clues before it's too late.

name: Hawkeye
title: 2021 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: Clint Barton and Kate Bishop shoot a few arrows and try to avoid becoming the target themselves.

name: WandaVision
title: 2021 ‧ Sitcom ‧ 1 season
description: Vision and Wanda live a normal life in Westview and conceal their superpowers. However, as decades pass by, they start doubting that everything is not what it seems.

name: Moon Knight
title: 2022 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: Steven Grant and mercenary Marc Spector investigate the mysteries of the Egyptian gods from inside the same body.

name: Loki
title: 2021 ‧ Action ‧ 2 seasons
description: After stealing the Tesseract, Loki comes into contact with a mysterious organization that gives him an ominous ultimatum, either fix the timeline or cease to exist completely.

name: Invincible
title: 2021 ‧ Drama ‧ 2 seasons
description: Seventeen-year-old Mark Grayson is just like every guy his age, except that his father is Omni-Man, the most powerful superhero on the planet. As Mark develops powers of his own, he discovers his father's legacy may not be as heroic as it seems.

name: Peacemaker
title: 2022 ‧ Action ‧ 1 season
description: After recovering from his injures, Christopher Smith is forced to join a black ops squad and eliminate parasites that have taken over human bodies around the world.

name: Skyfall
title: 2012 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 23m
description: An ex-MI6 agent steals a hard drive with top-secret information to carry out a vendetta on Bond's overseer. Later, Bond must face his past in a bid to try and save her.

name: Quantum of Solace
title: 2008 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 46m
description: An investigation leads James Bond on the trail of Dominic Greene, a renowned developer of green technology. When Dominic assists a coup in Bolivia to fulfil his intentions, Bond must save the day.

name: Casino Royale
title: 2006 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 24m
description: James Bond must prevent Le Chiffre, a banker to the world's most dangerous criminal organisations, from winning a high stakes poker game. He is assisted by Vesper Lynd, a British Treasury agent.

name: Spectre
title: 2015 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 28m
description: After receiving an encrypted message from a sinister organisation, with the help of Madeleine, James Bond sets out to uncover a conspiracy, which reveals an ugly truth about his past.

name: Die Another Day
title: 2002 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 13m
description: The link between a North Korean colonel and a nefarious diamond baron, who is subsidising the creation of a high-tech weapon, makes James Bond investigate the matter. But his mission gets sabotaged.

name: The World Is Not Enough
title: 1999 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 8m
description: When billionaire Robert King is assassinated, Bond is assigned to protect his daughter from the terrorist Renard. However, he soon uncovers Renard's sinister plot and he must act fast to save Europe.

name: Tomorrow Never Dies
title: 1997 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 1h 59m
description: James Bond, an undercover agent, sets out to prevent a media baron, Elliot Carver, from waging a war between China and the United Kingdom after he gets summoned by the Secret Intelligence Service.

name: GoldenEye
title: 1995 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 10m
description: James Bond teams up with computer programmer Natalia Simonava as he travels to Russia to locate an electromagnetic satellite weapon stolen by Alec, a former MI6 agent, who Bond believed was dead.

name: Licence to Kill
title: 1989 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 13m
description: James Bond and Felix Leiter capture drug lord Franz Sanchez, on the way to Leiter's wedding. But when Leiter is tortured and his bride is killed by Sanchez, Bond goes rogue in order to hunt him down.

name: The Living Daylights
title: 1987 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 10m
description: James Bond is assigned to facilitate the defection of KGB officer General Koskov. However, he realizes that bigger plans are in play when he discovers that Koskov's defection was staged.

name: Mission: Impossible – Ghost Protocol
title: 2011 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 13m
description: Ethan Hunt, an IMF agent, is recruited to lead Jane and Benji to infiltrate the Kremlin and locate files that will help identify Cobalt, who is out to instigate a nuclear war.

name: Mission: Impossible III
title: 2006 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 6m
description: Ethan Hunt is forced out of retirement to rescue his student captured by an arms dealer. His mission to rescue her not only gets his fiancee kidnapped but also exposes a mole in his organisation.

name: The Bourne Ultimatum
title: 2007 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 55m
description: Jason Bourne sets off on a quest to uncover his dark past. However, to get to the end of the riddle, he must dodge the CIA agents who're trying to kill him.

name: The Bourne Identity
title: 2002 ‧ Thriller/Action ‧ 1h 59m
description: A group of strangers find a man with bullet-ridden body and take care of him. He wakes up with a blank memory and begins a journey to learn his identity, unaware that the road ahead is full of danger.

name: The Bourne Supremacy
title: 2004 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 48m
description: Jason Bourne is forced to return to his old ways as an assassin after his girlfriend Marie is killed. Deputy Director Pamela Landy investigates the connection between Bourne and Operation Treadstone.

name: The Dark Knight
title: 2008 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 2h 32m
description: Batman has a new foe, the Joker, who is an accomplished criminal hell-bent on decimating Gotham City. Together with Gordon and Harvey Dent, Batman struggles to thwart the Joker before it is too late.

name: Batman Begins
title: 2005 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 2h 20m
description: After witnessing his parents' death, Bruce learns the art of fighting to confront injustice. When he returns to Gotham as Batman, he decides to stop a secret society that intends to destroy the city.

name: The Batman
title: 2022 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 2h 56m
description: Batman is called to intervene when the mayor of Gotham City is murdered. Soon, his investigation leads him to uncover a web of corruption, linked to his own dark past.

name: Kingsman: The Secret Service
title: 2014 ‧ Action/Comedy ‧ 2h 9m
description: Anti-social and unemployed, Eggsy Unwin faces several challenges when he gets recruited as a secret agent in a secret spy organisation in order to look for Richmond Valentine, an eco-terrorist.

name: Deadpool 2
title: 2018 ‧ Action/Comedy ‧ 2 hours
description: Deadpool protects a young mutant Russell from the authorities and gets thrown in prison. However, he escapes and forms a team of mutants to prevent a time-travelling mercenary from killing Russell.

name: From Russia with Love
title: 1963 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 55m
description: James Bond searches for a Lektor cryptographic device that has the potential to wreak havoc in the world and stops SPECTRE, a secret crime organisation, from acquiring it.

name: Goldfinger
title: 1964 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 1h 50m
description: MI6 agent James Bond investigates a gold-smuggling ring run by businessman Auric Goldfinger. As he delves deeper into his activities, he uncovers a sinister plan to attack Fort Knox's gold reserves.

name: Thunderball
title: 1965 ‧ Action/Thriller ‧ 2h 10m
description: Phantom, a criminal organization, plans to threaten the United Nations and steal nuclear weapons from the NATO base. Things take a turn when James Bond sets out to nab the criminals.

name: For Your Eyes Only
title: 1981 ‧ Action/Adventure ‧ 2h 7m
description: After a British information-gathering vessel sinks into the sea, Agent 007 is given the responsibility of locating the lost encryption device and thwarting it from entering inimical hands.

name: Bridge of Spies
title: 2015 ‧ Thriller/War ‧ 2h 22m
description: James B Donovan defends an alleged KGB spy, Rudolf Abel, in the US courts. He is eventually called upon to negotiate an exchange of Rudolf with a US pilot, Francis Powers, who was caught in the USSR.

name: Johnny English
title: 2003 ‧ Comedy/Family ‧ 1h 29m
description: After all the MI5 agents are killed following an attack, Johnny English, an intellectually challenged yet confident spy, decides to operate all the missions of the department single-handedly.

name: The Monster Squad
title: 1987 ‧ Horror/Comedy ‧ 1h 22m
description: Count Dracula and other monsters are on a hunt to seize an amulet that will grant them powers to rule the world. That is when the young boys' Monster Squad reveals its devious plan to curb the evil.

name: Tales from the Crypt: Demon Knight
title: 1995 ‧ Horror/Fantasy ‧ 1h 33m
description: Trouble ensues when Frank Brayker gets into an accident and takes shelter in a decommissioned church. Later, he is chased by a demon called the Collector who uses him to fulfil his devilish needs.

name: Death Race 2000
title: 1975 ‧ Sci-fi/Action ‧ 1h 24m
description: Under the dictatorship of Mr President, a brutally violent race rewards the fastest driver who claims the most victims, until a group of Thomas Paine's descendants revolts.

name: 2 Fast 2 Furious
title: 2003 ‧ Action/Crime ‧ 1h 47m
description: Brian O'Conner, a former police officer, partners with Roman Pierce, his friend and a criminal, to bring a drug lord to justice in order to erase their criminal record.

name: Resident Evil: Afterlife
title: 2010 ‧ Horror/Action ‧ 1h 40m
description: Alice leads a group of survivors to Arcadia, a safe haven somewhere in Alaska. Once there, they learn that the place is being used as a trap to lure more survivors and infect them with the T-virus.

name: Apocalypse Now
title: 1979 ‧ War/Action ‧ 2h 33m
description: Captain Willard is sent to Cambodia on a dangerous mission to assassinate a renegade colonel who has won the trust of a local tribe.

name: The Godfather
title: 1972 ‧ Crime/Crime ‧ 2h 55m
description: Don Vito Corleone, head of a mafia family, decides to hand over his empire to his youngest son, Michael. However, his decision unintentionally puts the lives of his loved ones in grave danger.

name: The Great Escape
title: 1963 ‧ War/Adventure ‧ 2h 52m
description: Imprisoned Allied soldiers plot their escape from a German camp to force Nazi soldiers away from the battle during WWII. However, they soon find that the stakes are much higher than they anticipated.

name: Full Metal Jacket
title: 1987 ‧ War/Action ‧ 1h 56m
description: A pragmatic US Marine observes the degenerating effects of the brutal Vietnam War on his fellow recruits from the days of the severe boot camp training to the senseless street fights in Hue.

name: The Eagle Has Landed
title: 1976 ‧ War/Thriller ‧ 2h 25m
description: During World War II, the Nazis devise a secret plan to kidnap Winston Churchill through a daring mission led by disgruntled but righteous Nazi officer Oberst Kurt Steiner.

name: Back to the Future
title: 1985 ‧ Family/Sci-fi ‧ 1h 56m
description: In the 1980s, an experiment by a weird scientist turns out to be faulty. It leads to his teenaged pal going back in time to the 1950s where he is forced to reunite the younger version of his parents.

name: A Bridge Too Far
title: 1977 ‧ War/Action ‧ 2h 59m
description: The Allied armies concocted a plan to win the World War II at Arnhem. Disaster ensues when the area around Arnhem, including the key bridges of Germany, is loaded with armoured assaults.

name: Das Boot
title: 1981 ‧ War/Thriller ‧ 2h 29m
